msgstr "Versione dell'immagine: ``8.7.1``"

#: ../../release_notes.rst:18 5e8131e3c1834a5a8a6ba9ee371af5b3
msgid ""
"Fixed issue where dnsmasq could be stopped by keepalived even when not in HA"
